{"tid":2154778,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"擱 筆 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-08-13T10:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T10:23:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a604b06a521a55a28fc2f89f49fba3c2b274ccf","tid":2154778,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200719/3HEEGPPLVNDZJHA6JS3BUMVIQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200719%2F3HEEGPPLVNDZJHA6JS3BUMVIQY%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzgDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=3da245e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200719%2F3HEEGPPLVNDZJHA6JS3BUMVIQY%2F&h=e82ecd0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200719/3HEEGPPLVNDZJHA6JS3BUMVIQY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n擱 筆 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S-4XmJWK7EeFGcllQH7gJadPfhY=/1049x711/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SPUZKKCMVNHNNCYK4BMHDXIWIY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS-4XmJWK7EeFGcllQH7gJadPfhY%3D%2F1049x711%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSPUZKKCMVNHNNCYK4BMHDXIWIY.png&h=4626d140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n七月初，「香港區國安法」通過之後，我要繼續無所顧忌議論大政，是不可能的了，唯有告別《蘋果日報》論壇版，有人贊同，但也有人相嘲說：「寫真話有那麼困難嗎？」難不難，其實要看真話的標準。巴金晚年都自稱「寫真話」。<br />\n<br />\n不談大政，就留在《蘋果》名采版論小政吧。但是，八月十日，新香港警察二百人浩浩蕩蕩，直闖《蘋果》報館，大舉搜查；《蘋果》主腦黎智英、張劍虹等五人被捕，還有黎智英兩個兒子都不免。然則小政看來都不能論了，以後，就談談中英文，寫寫小雜感好了。<br />\n<br />\n一九八零年十月十二日，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。四十年前，我也想不到會有今日之日，須擱下議政之筆。<br />\n<br />\n張劍虹說：「《蘋果》一定可以撐下去。」他說話時，給警察緊緊抓住，雙手銬於背後，令人見之鼻酸。我想，《蘋果》撐不下去，也不要緊。這分報紙就是一管直筆。此筆一擱，應比二百警察包圍報館更能轟動天下。"}]}